伦敦 O2 体育场因拒绝穿着“自由加沙”衬衫的男子入场而道歉https://www.nme.com/news/music/london-o2-arena-apologises-for-refusing-man-entry-over-free-gaza-shirt-3784636?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=london-o2-竞技场为拒绝男子穿着自由加沙衬衫进入而道歉Laura MolloySun, 18 Aug 2024 07:59:32 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3784636 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 O2 体育场。图片来源：詹姆斯·钱斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该场馆表示他们正在审查未来的政策</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/london-o2-arena-apologises-for-refusing-man-entry-over-free-gaza-shirt-3784636">伦敦 O2 体育场因拒绝穿着“自由加沙”衬衫的男子入场而道歉</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 O2 体育场。图片来源：詹姆斯·钱斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The-O2-Arena-London.-Credit_-James-Chance_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦 O2 体育场在拒绝一名身穿“自由加沙”衬衫的男子入场后道歉。</p><p>上周六（8 月 10 日），一对夫妇试图在会场观看<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-kay">Peter Kay 的</a>现场表演，但被保安拒绝进入，保安认为他的 T 恤违反政策。</p><p>这名男子被要求再买一件T恤换上，但他将T恤翻过来的要求被拒绝了，保安说这件T恤必须留在他们身边，不能进入会场。</p><p>另一位保安人员告诉这对夫妇，O2 是一个“非政治场所”，对此类口号采取“中立”立场。</p><p> O2 体育场的所有者 AEG Europe 公司后来告诉<a href="https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/20240815-london-o2-arena-refuses-entry-to-man-over-free-gaza-shirt-prompting-boycott-calls/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《中东观察》</em></a> ，这对夫妇被拒绝是因为场馆的“违禁物品”政策，该政策禁止“我们合理认为可能对任何人造成危险或干扰的物品”。活动或其他访客。”</p><p>该事件的视频随后在网上流传，引发了抵制该场馆的呼声。</p><p>现在，O2 发表声明称，他们“对此次事件可能造成的任何冒犯和不安表示诚挚的歉意”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">他因穿着写有“自由加沙”的 T 恤而被拒绝进入 O2。 <a href="https://t.co/ZYUInPamD7">pic.twitter.com/ZYUInPamD7</a></p><p> — 穆赫塔尔 (@I_amMukhtar) <a href="https://twitter.com/I_amMukhtar/status/1824416378645844073?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 16 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>声明中写道：“在任何一个晚上，我们都会接待多达 20,000 人，我们会尽力根据现有信息及时做出最佳决策。” “我们并不是每次都做出正确的决定，这一次我们做出了判断，但结果是错误的。为此，我们深表歉意。”</p><p>他们接着说：“安全和保障始终是我们的首要任务，我们竭尽全力为所有客人提供一个安全和受尊重的环境。正是出于这个原因，我们存在“违禁物品”政策，并在我们所有活动的条款和条件中进行了规定。</p><p>声明称，场馆的政策是禁止携带可能对任何活动或其他游客造成危险或干扰的物品，但他们承认，这次情况并非如此。 “进入应该被批准，”他们说。</p><p>他们继续说道：“为了明确起见，没有任何场馆政策禁止服装显示任何特定信息，除非我们有理由相信存在干扰风险或这是非法的。”</p><p>他们最后表示，他们将审查未来的政策和程序，“以防止这种情况再次发生”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-yN7hQsBCi/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563