www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bryan_Steffy_Tim_Mosenfelder_Gabe_Ginsberg_Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bryan_Steffy_Tim_Mosenfelder_Gabe_Ginsberg_Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bryan_Steffy_Tim_Mosenfelder_Gabe_Ginsberg_Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bryan_Steffy_Tim_Mosenfelder_Gabe_Ginsberg_Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bryan_Steffy_Tim_Mosenfelder_Gabe_Ginsberg_Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-found-glory">New Found Glory</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bowling-for-soup">Bowling For Soup</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/plain-white-ts">Plain White T&#39;s</a>等艺术家将为一张全流行朋克<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">迪士尼</a>翻唱专辑贡献歌曲。</p><p> “A Whole New Sound”将于 9 月 6 日发行，由流行朋克乐队重新演绎的迪士尼歌曲集中的经典歌曲组成。</p><p>参与该项目的其他艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-plan">Simple Plan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/meet-me-at-the-altar">Meet Me @ The Altar</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/magnolia-park">Magnolia Park</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yellowcard">Yellowcard</a> 。</p><p>合辑中分享的最新单曲是 New Found Glory 版本的“Part Of Your World”，这是 1989 年<i>《小美人鱼》</i>中深受喜爱的曲目。</p><p>在这里听听他们的版本： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="新发现的荣耀 - 你世界的一部分（来自“全新声音”）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KuxZUwq9LFA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3784605" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784605" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784605" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/disney_new_found_glory-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784605" class="wp-caption-text">迪士尼“全新声音”再获荣耀。图片来源：迪士尼</figcaption></figure><p>乐队的吉他手查德·吉尔伯特 (Chad Gilbert) 表示：“在创作这首歌的过程中，我花了一段时间思考歌词和旋律。我意识到，为了让人们感受到爱丽儿的感受，我们需要将音乐的能量与歌曲中叛逆的思想以及她对冒险的希望相匹配。当她唱起想要跳舞的歌时，音乐欢快而有趣，但当她表达对自由的渴望时，节奏就下降了，所以你真的能感受到心脏的牵引力。”</p><p> “我们乐队的最大目标一直是向年轻人展示和鼓励年轻人，心态年轻的人，以及任何有梦想但面临自我怀疑的人，因为外面的世界会接受他们本来的样子。不要害怕采取下一步。”</p><h2> <strong>“全新声音”的完整曲目列表是：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="426" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>新发现的荣耀——“你世界的一部分”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="426" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsi